n比大陸捉好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸有背景就唔會捉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦 大陸犯毒品罪 幾大都只有死路一條<br />\n唔好再以幾十年前舊式思維去諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/024634_5357df3b8925b3c1779ce5af9d52478b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F024634_5357df3b8925b3c1779ce5af9d52478b.jpg&h=bc1ea645&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/024637_5072659a481cdd569ac8aa4699504093.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F024637_5072659a481cdd569ac8aa4699504093.jpg&h=fcc2d1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知呢班人喺支那犯毒品罪又使唔使死呢？</blockquote><br />\n中國有個大毒梟係江澤民近親，無人敢捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}